{"tid":2345900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼國Epic官方App令CPU溫度暴升　網民：向神秘網址送出數據","createTime":"2020-12-30T01:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T05:16:16.000Z","uid":26770,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"212eefc73627b787a4a9e6c519e5e3511efb84ed","tid":2345900,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/29/rumors-epic-games-program-increases-the-cpu-temperature-and-uses-the-cpu-to-send-data-to-the-mysterious-website/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F29%2Frumors-epic-games-program-increases-the-cpu-temperature-and-uses-the-cpu-to-send-data-to-the-mysterious-website%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=dae3012c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/29/rumors-epic-games-program-increases-the-cpu-temperature-and-uses-the-cpu-to-send-data-to-the-mysterious-website/tech-secure/</a><br />\nEpic Games 最近連日向玩家送贈不同種類的遊戲，只要登記用戶就能領取，不過近日有 Epic Games Store 玩家在 Reddit 上反饋指在打機時遇到問題，指 Epic Games Store 程式會導致部分 AMD 和 Intel CPU 的溫度不明地上升<br />\n<br />\n有用戶在 Reddit 上指他所使用的 AMD Ryzen 7 5800X CPU 在關閉 Epic Games Launcher 後溫度從 50 度下降到 37 度，因此懷疑 Epic Games Launcher 在後台佔用了 CPU 資源，部分甚至沒有運行任何遊戲。另外，有部分 Intel CPU 用戶發現了 Epic Games Launcher 亦同樣導致電腦出現類似情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<span class=\"red\">呢個咪係外國班後生勁奶共真相<br />\nEpic派game, 大量咩9中國手機app送娛樂<br />\n<br />\n班撚樣心諗香港人,中國人人權幾慘都唔關自己事</span>"},{"pid":"3b7d62f38fbb6d786aace9416be0eda4ad771e05","tid":2345900,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"免費係最貴"},{"pid":"f4278f41fa18ba97c73002329523d0af6f7f3adb","tid":2345900,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"後生仔未出去打工,或者工作經驗少未升上頂<br />\n有人送錢比自己一定話好好好<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">大量外國人就係袋左呢種利益所以幫中共護航</span><b